"<strong>Six. Tacit extension.</strong>\n"
"                        Once five (5) years of duration of the contract have\n"
"                        elapsed at minimum, if neither the Lessee notifies the\n"
"                        Lessor of their intention not to renew with two (2)\n"
"                        months notice, nor the Lessor notifies the Lessee with\n"
"                        four (4) months notice, the contract shall be\n"
"                        obligatorily extended for annual periods up to a\n"
"                        maximum of three (3) additional years."
