"<strong>Twelve. Lessee's works.</strong>\n"
"                        The Lessee may not carry out works that modify the\n"
"                        configuration of the dwelling or any of its\n"
"                        accessories without the Lessor's written consent.\n"
"                        Authorised works shall be carried out at the Lessee's\n"
"                        expense and, at the end of the contract, shall remain\n"
"                        for the benefit of the property without generating any\n"
"                        right to compensation. Contravention of this clause\n"
"                        shall be cause for resolution of the contract."
